latestPosts.caption:
Chapter 2 took another baby step and you made it feel like a giant leap 🚀

OPEN NOW: Linking Road, Bandra.

#Chapter2 #Brick&Mortar #Flagship

Who would’ve thought, 5 years ago, that we’ll be standing here, bruised not broken - with our very first retail store.
Chapter2 was born not because we were fashion enthusiasts. It came to life when it felt like life wasn’t the same anymore. It did not start as a place that sells clothes, it started as an emotion, a voice for everyone to resonate with. 
The past 15 months, leading up to this day feels nothing but surreal. I just wanted to write this to tell you that we are standing here today. It wasn’t easy and it’s not going to be easy but it’s worth it. 
Do not, just do not give up. Give it your all and i promise you it is worth it.
This is us writing our sequel. It’s time you write yours too. We are here. We are here to stay and we welcome you  without any judgement. We welcome you to celebrate change, to laugh together, to cry when the going gets tough, to normalise change.
Change is dynamic and we as humans adapt as quickly. Let’s learn how to accept it.
This is Chapter2Drip.
Thank you to everyone who has been part of this journey, who believes in us and has supported us  everyday. 
#Justthebeggining
#dreamsdocometrue 

Special mention to our dear friend and store conceptualiser @roopagram ♥️

THIS IS FREEDOM

#Chapter2
